          "chunk_id": "a9846820-f923-55e3-aa20-fcdeaea439a8",
          "page_number": 1,
          "section_heading": "DESIGN",
          "text": "DESIGN\n\nThe low-power prototype sampled IMU motion at 50 Hz to reduce energy use. The report\ndoes not evaluate diagnostic performance."
        }
      ],
